description.manufacturer: Kuat Drive Yards, Allanteen Six Shipyards
description.description:
The Venator-class Star Destroyer, also known as the Venator-class Destroyer, Republic attack cruiser,[3] and later Imperial attack cruiser,
 was one of the capital ships used extensively by the Galactic Republic during the later parts of the Clone Wars, as well as
 by the Galactic Empire. It was designed and constructed by Kuat Drive Yards and Allanteen Six shipyards.
